Package: bcops
Type: Package
Title: BCOPS (balanced&conformal optimal prediction set)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Leying Guan, Rob Tibshirani
Maintainer: Leying Guan <leying.guan@yale.edu>
Description: Perform BCOPS for classification problems when the unlabeled test data are available. 
    BCOPS is a model-free classification approach that is good at both making accurate predictions and refrain from making predictions for test samples that are far from the training data, even in high dimension.
License: GPL-2
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp (>= 0.11.0), glmnet, MASS, Matrix, foreach, ranger, ks
NeedsCompilation: yes
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
